Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:13.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好了各位 奴隸和宮女嬪妃\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Okay, people. Slavers and harem concubines--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:16.26,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,準備上場\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:19.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這是給你的 他寫的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}This is for you. From him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,小美人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Bellissima. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:54.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你來了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.86,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,請吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.37,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我真高興你願意來找我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I am so pleased you agreed to join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.87,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你知道的 我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You see, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.61,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我總是只能一個人吃晚飯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I often must dine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-你嗎 -恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- You? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.38,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,真難以置信\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:12.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這對我來說實在是煎熬 你知道嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Well, it's not simple for me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,名和利\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Fame is its own kind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,只是另一種枷鎖罷了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}of, uh, prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,請坐\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.61,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這面龐真是驚為天人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It's a wonderful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你竟然會說意大利語\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You speak Italian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,能聽得懂\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Well, I understand it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.54,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我來自本森赫斯特\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm from Bensonhurst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.67,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我小時候周圍的人都只說意大利語\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Italian's all my folks talked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我爸爸來自西西里島\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}when I was growing up. Pop's from Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.71,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-他是個水管工 -恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- He's a plumber. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.39,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,所以你懷揣著成為女演員的夢想\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And you have come to Hollywood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.78,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,來到了好萊塢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}with dreams of becoming an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這真不幸\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That is unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:59.32,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我覺得你可以比這個更加偉大\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I think I see greater things in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,比不朽還要偉大\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Greater than being immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為我覺得在大銀幕上表演就意味著不朽\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}'Cause that's what it means to be up on that screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:11.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,只是個影子\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Shadows only.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,頂多一個世紀\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}A hundred years and no one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,人們就不會記得我們做過什麼了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}will remember what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No, I don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.44,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我完全不同意\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't agree at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:24.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我覺得電影就是未來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I think the flickers are the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這是一種真正的美國藝術\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}A true American art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.56,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你才是真正的美國藝術\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You are a true American art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.23,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你是在取笑我嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不不不 小姑娘\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No, no, no, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.23,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我是在 讚美你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I am, uh... admiring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.00,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,真抱歉 如果你誤解了我的意思\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm sorry. If it seems otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那全都是因為\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}it is only because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:48.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我的英語不好\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}my English is not so good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在無需語言的方面\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I do better
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我可以做的更好\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}without words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:08.56,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.64,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.74,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這就是那隻小老鼠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}this is the mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.51,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,喔天哪 你是\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh, my God, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.08,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我是貓\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.68,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,小老鼠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}little mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.95,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這是我妻子 娜塔莎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}This is my wife, Natacha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:07.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,蘭波娃\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Rambova.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我真的 真的很抱歉 我以為\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I am... so sorry, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我在和丈夫鬧離婚嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That I was divorcing my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:16.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,沒錯呀\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And so I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我 我該走了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I sh...should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:22.08,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不不不 別這麼著急呀\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No, no, no. Please, not yet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,別走\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.03,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,娜塔莎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Natacha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.74,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你對我們的客人溫柔一點 好嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}you must be gentle with our guest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,離婚只是一場戲\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The divorce is for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,多年以來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The studio has been trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,片方都想要把我們倆拆散\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}tear us apart for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.85,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,所以我們決定\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We have decided the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.08,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,唯一能夠在一起的辦法就是\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}we can really be together is if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,讓全世界都以為我們不在一起了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the world thinks we are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.19,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,為什麼要我來這\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為 小老鼠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Because, little mouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,人總有七情六慾嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}...gods have appetites.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.12,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我聽說他不光有錢 而且還單身\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I hear he's not only rich, but single
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.76,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,還超帥 可真棒呀\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}and handsome, so far as that goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.53,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-你怎麼認識他的 -我還沒跟他見過面呢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- How'd you meet this guy, anyway? - I haven't met him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.59,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,城裏沒有哪個摩登女郎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}There isn't a flapper in this city who hasn't been invited
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,沒被他邀請去私人派對的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}to one of his private wingdings. You'd know that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,要不是你整個夏天都沒在圈裏混 你早就知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}if you hadn't been out of circulation all summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.67,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我一直都在\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I've been around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.14,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好吧 我忍不住了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Okay, I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.48,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我真的很想問 你一直跑去見誰啊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}So spill-- who have you been seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.32,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,沒誰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,撒謊 你可騙不了我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Lies. You can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.88,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你戀愛了 不是嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You're in love, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.79,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我很高興歡迎諸位來到科爾特茲旅館的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'd like to welcome you all to the opening week
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.86,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,開業周活動\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}of the Hotel Cortez!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.19,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,很遺憾我們不能\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}A shame we can't all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.69,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在我的新藍鸚鵡廳裏\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}enjoy these libations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,享受開酒儀式\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}in my new Blue Parrot Lounge, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,除非有誰良心發現把那該死的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}until someone with some sense repeals that nasty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,禁酒法案給廢掉\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Volstead Act,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.00,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不然我和卡朋先生\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}both I and Mr. Capone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,就只能將就了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}will have to make due.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.88,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,阿\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.05,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.85,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,瓦倫蒂諾死了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Valentino's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:11.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他今天早晨在紐約去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He died in New York this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.36,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他的電影剛剛上映\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And his movie just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.43,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我賭票房肯定大賣\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Bet the box office goes through the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.56,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你的心臟跳的像蜂鳥一樣快\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Your heart's beating like a hummingbird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.63,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,放開我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.44,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不 我不會放開你的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No. I don't suppose I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噓\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,實際上\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我可能永遠也不會放你走\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I may never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,真是太悲慘了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It's just so... tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們好像錯過她了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I guess we missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,誰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,黑衣女郎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The Lady in Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,幾個月來她每天都會來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}She's been coming here for months every day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,留下一支紅色玫瑰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}and leaving a single red rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我以為那只是傳聞而已\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I thought that was a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.70,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不 是真的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這裏寫的很清楚\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It says so right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,「有謠言稱神秘人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Rumors have sprung up of a mysterious figure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,到訪瓦倫蒂諾之墓」\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Visiting Valentino's tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:02.77,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,「有位黑衣女郎 在瓦倫蒂諾八月離世後\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"The Lady In Black has left a single red rose
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,每天在這位偉大的情聖的墓旁\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Next to the Great Lover's final resting place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,放一支紅色玫瑰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Each day since his death last August.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:12.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,有人說這位帶面紗的女士是女演員寶拉·內歌裏\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Some say the veiled figure is movie actress Pola Negri,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,眾所周知 她曾在瓦倫提諾的婚禮上歇斯底里地爆發」\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}who famously collapsed at Valentino's funeral."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,婊子 她可沒愛過他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Harlot. She never loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:21.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,「還有人相信這位沉默探望者\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"Others believed the wordless visitor is something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,並非地球生物」\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}something not of this Earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好吧 為了賣雜誌他們什麼都能掰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Well, they'll print anything to sell magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,呃 女士們\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Uh... ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:40.58,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,也許我們該迴避一下\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Maybe we should give her her privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.11,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你為何流淚\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why do you weep so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,小老鼠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}little mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.37,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,娜塔莎 這段時間你都在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Natacha. Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,到處走走\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.87,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我給你寫信了 好多封 你從沒有回信\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I wrote to you, so many times-- I never heard back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你連他的葬禮都沒有來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You didn't even come to his funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:15.51,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我為何要去一個活人的葬禮\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why would I go to the funeral of a man who isn't dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,小美人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Bellisima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你死了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.70,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,然後我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.94,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,重生了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.44,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那墓裏的不是魯迪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The body in that crypt isn't Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.74,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是我了不起的替身 喬治·菲斯克\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It's my stunt double, George Fiske.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.63,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-永遠這麼忠誠 -即使是死這件事\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- Always so loyal. - Even in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.95,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但是要說明的是 我的表演大多是真刀真槍的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Though to be clear, I did do most of my own stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,只不過這次不是\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Just not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:52.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你偽造了你的死亡\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You faked your death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我愛你們兩個\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I loved you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而你們就讓我以為你真的死了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And you just let me think the worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.39,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我差點悲傷而死\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I almost didn't survive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.59,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但你沒有\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But you did survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.56,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而且你很快走出來了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And in some style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.76,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,順祝你新婚愉快\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Congratulations on the nuptials, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這麼快就找到了下一任\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.70,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你想怎樣\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.73,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在這個世界上我孤身一人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was all alone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我決定\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I decided that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:17.54,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,如果我注定要悲傷度過餘生\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}if I was to live in grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.14,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我也想\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I might as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,被美麗的東西\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}be surrounded by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,環繞\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}beautiful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.32,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,即使要跟一個\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Even if it was with a man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.09,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我根本沒感覺的男人在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}for whom I felt... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我被拖入他內心深處的無邊黑暗中\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was drawn to the darkness I felt within him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.79,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,被婚姻\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I ached...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,消耗\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我是如此痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}consumed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,親愛的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.77,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你真是激發我所有的潛能啊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}you are a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.94,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他使我發現了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He uncovered in me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.14,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,自己身上前所未見的東西\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}things I never thought possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.18,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他是誰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,就是個流浪漢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Just a hobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.69,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你不同意\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You disapprove?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.67,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你為何要浪費時間殺幾個窮要飯的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why waste your time killing some destitute beggar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:21.87,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這樣有什麼好處\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What's to be gained?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.77,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,選一個有錢或者珠寶的獵物\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Select a victim with money or jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:27.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這樣你的小愛好就能使我們倆都獲益\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Then your little hobby can benefit us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,下一次\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.38,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我想看著你做\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}...I want to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你經歷了太多痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You have suffered too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.72,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不覺得痛苦\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.29,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-不再覺得痛苦了 -你的眼淚告訴我你在說謊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- Not anymore. - Your tears tell me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我沒有任何感覺\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I feel nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:53.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們不是想要拋棄你 小姑娘\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We never meant to leave you this way, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:59.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那你們為什麼要那麼做\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Then why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:02.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,造化弄人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Fate intervened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.71,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我在全國到處跑\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was travelling the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,宣傳《酋長之子》\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}promoting Son of the Sheik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:08.08,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在新世紀公司的列車上旅行\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Booked on the 20th Century Limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,從舊金山一直到紐約\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the tour would take me from San Francisco to New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:13.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,每一站都被媒體圍追堵截\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}with press stops all along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:18.32,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我開始留意一個每一站都出現的男人 最開始\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}At each stop, I began to notice a man. At first,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:19.89,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我以為他也是報社的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I thought he was a member of the press,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但他從不問任何問題\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}but he never asked any questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:24.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,也不寫任何筆記 他只是注視著我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}never wrote anything down. He just watched me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:27.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他的眼神從不離開我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}his eyes never leaving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.34,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這當然很不尋常\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}This was not unusual, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但那雙眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But something in those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.77,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,讓人著迷\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在火車上 我總是覺得\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Again on the train, I began to feel a presence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.94,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,有什麼東西讓我毛骨悚然\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}which raised the hairs on the back of my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我感覺在整列火車上\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I imagined I was seeing him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.48,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,到處都是他的影子\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}all throughout the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我開始懷疑我是不是出問題了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I began to doubt my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:57.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,恐懼像裹屍布一樣圍繞著我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}A feeling of dread hung over me like a shroud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而有一天\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:02.26,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在中西部無盡的平原上行駛的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}along an endless expanse of Midwest plains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:06.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我從無夢的睡眠中醒來 卻彷彿踏入了夢境中\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I woke from a dreamless sleep into a dream itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.94,0:22:11.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那是一種誘惑 但是肉慾卻不是他的目的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It was a seduction, but mere carnality was not his aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.94,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,電光火石間我便無法自拔\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was repelled and drawn in all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當他開口時 他說的是摻雜著濃濃德國口音\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When he spoke, it was in Italian
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:19.58,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,的意大利語\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}but with a thick German accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他告訴我他的名字是F·W·穆爾諾\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He revealed to me his name, F.W. Murnau,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:26.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,一位德國大導演\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the great German director.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他想要你幹什麼呢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What did he want from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.53,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我以為他想殺了我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I thought he meant to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:34.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但他其實是想讓我「留存」下來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But instead he wished to preserve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,一開始我也不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Neither did I, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:40.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在完成他的傑作《不死殭屍》的過程中\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The great director had uncovered many secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:44.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這位偉大的導演發現了許多秘密\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}in the making of his masterpiece, Nosferatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:47.14,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,為了完成他的影片 他深入到\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}To make his picture, he travelled deep
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:49.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,喀爾巴阡山脈之中\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}into the Carpathian Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:52.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他追求真實性\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He demanded authenticity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:56.15,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那也正是他在那片古老的世界中找到的東西\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}and that is what he found in that Old World.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.39,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他在銀幕上所描繪的那種生物\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Creatures like the one he was depicting onscreen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:02.29,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不像他的男主角馬科斯·夏瑞克那樣可怕\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}though not hideous like his star, Max Schreck,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:05.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,反而是無與倫比的美麗\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}but beautiful beyond compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:07.86,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,被一種古老的血液病毒所感染\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Infected with an ancient blood virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,其結果就是永生\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the consequence of which was eternal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,永葆青春\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}endless youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但也會產生一種可怕的飢渴\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But also a terrible thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.37,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他說告訴我所有這一切 是一種預告\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He was telling me all this, he said, as a prelude,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:23.51,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,既是警告的預告 也是禮物的饋贈\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}a prelude to a warning and the offer of a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:27.71,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,茂瑙對我哀嘆\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Murnau lamented to me what he foresees,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:29.98,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他預剪到有聲電影的到來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the coming of talking pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:33.59,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而這意味著諸神的死亡\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And with that, the death of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:38.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在最多一年之內 我們的世界將會消亡\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Within a year, no more, our world would be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他說 他不能拯救這個世界 但他能拯救我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He couldn't save the world, he said, but he could save me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:44.23,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,讓我永葆美麗\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}preserve my beauty for all eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.03,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但是我得離開銀幕才行\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}but only if I was ready to leave the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,永遠離開\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,所以 一個冰冷的碰觸\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And so, with a cool touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,和一個溫暖的親吻之後 我真正的自由了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}and a warm kiss, I was truly free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.88,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我是不死的 不再只是一個影子\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Immortal. No longer just a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:58.38,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當我抵達紐約的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When I arrived in New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:00.91,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,媒體報道稱我病了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}the press reported that I had fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.72,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我讓他們相信了這個傳聞 我知道這些報道\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I let them believe it, knowing the reports
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:07.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,正是我需要的 它們可以讓娜塔莎飛到我的身邊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}were all I would need to have Natacha fly to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:11.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當她來到我身邊時\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When she came to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:14.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我與她分享了茂瑙贈予我的黑暗禮物\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I shared with her the dark gift Murnau had given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:17.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,現在我們想與你一起分享它\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And now we want to share it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:20.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,和我們一起走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Come away with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:22.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,有一趟明晚出發到紐約的火車\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}There's a train that leaves tomorrow night to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:25.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,從那裏可以去歐洲 任何地方\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}From there, to Europe. Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:26.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,每個地方\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:39.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.32,0:24:41.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.55,0:24:44.56,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,永遠這樣\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.13,0:24:51.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我想你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:12.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你聽說了關於舌頭那個謀殺案嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You hear the one about the tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:15.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,兇手用鋸子把受害者的舌頭鋸斷\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Cut out of the victim's head with a hacksaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.53,0:25:17.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,然後用錘子把它釘在地板上\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}then nailed to the floor with a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.48,0:25:19.15,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她當時還活著呢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}While she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:20.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,嚇死人了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You're freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:22.72,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那個變態就在這兒 就在那扇門後面嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That monster is here, right behind that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.46,0:25:26.43,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣的變態才會想到那種噁心事\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What kind of psycho thinks of that shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.36,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,更別說這麼做了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Much less do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.40,0:25:31.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那他們只讓一個守衛守門嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And they only have one guard at the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.63,0:25:35.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我能搞定任何狀況\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm plenty enough for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.50,0:25:36.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你最好留心那扇門\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You better pay attention to that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:38.67,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,確保沒有任何壞東西跑出來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}make sure nothing bad comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:07.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟 你還好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Hey, man, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.70,0:27:15.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你是誰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.60,0:27:18.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我是雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm Wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.28,0:27:27.91,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你沒吃你的晚飯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You didn't eat your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:29.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不想吃那個\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm not hungry for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.85,0:27:32.32,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他們也可以給你弄點別的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}They can get you something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:35.59,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不想再吃東西了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't want to feed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.59,0:27:43.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他們為什麼把你關在這 雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why did they put you in here, Wren?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:45.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為我不和他們說話\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Because I wouldn't talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.70,0:27:47.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,警察嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.96,0:27:50.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,哈恩偵探\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Detective Hahn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.48,0:28:03.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他們在電視台找到的你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}They found you at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.08,0:28:05.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你目睹了發生的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.48,0:28:07.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我幫忙了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.58,0:28:11.39,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你一定被嚇壞了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You must have been terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.42,0:28:12.95,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你看見的那個人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The man you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.99,0:28:15.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,做了很多壞事\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}has done a lot of bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.99,0:28:19.37,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,醜陋 可怕的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Ugly, scary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.80,0:28:24.10,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但是你再也不用害怕他了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But you don't have to be afraid of him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.13,0:28:26.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你相信嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:28.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我相信\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.84,0:28:31.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但是沒人強迫我做任何事情\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But nobody forced me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.81,0:28:41.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噢 上帝啊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh, sweet Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,別動\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.10,0:28:56.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.10,0:28:59.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你殺了保安\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You killed the security guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.50,0:29:01.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他打算抓住他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He was going to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.07,0:29:09.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我希望我們能夠信任彼此 雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I want to know we can trust each other, Wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.28,0:29:13.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不會對你撒謊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I won't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:19.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你能對我做同樣的承諾嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Can you promise the same to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.30,0:29:23.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,另外幾次我也在那兒\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was there the other times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.19,0:29:26.23,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他把那些人的舌頭釘在桌子上的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When he nailed their tongues to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.26,0:29:28.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他把那對兄弟在床上吊死的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When he hung the brothers from the beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:32.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他切開了他們的肚子\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He cut open their stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.23,0:29:34.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那味道真是噁心\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It stunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:38.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你現在相信我嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Now do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.87,0:29:42.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你在那兒\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:49.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但是無論他讓你做什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But whatever he made you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.78,0:29:54.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,無論你認為你做了什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}whatever you think you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.49,0:29:56.29,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,都是他的責任\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}he's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.34,0:30:00.46,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不是你的錯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.49,0:30:03.73,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是我的錯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.76,0:30:05.86,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,發生的每件事情\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.90,0:30:07.10,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,拜託\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.13,0:30:10.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,別這麼說\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.17,0:30:13.91,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你聽起來就像我的女兒斯嘉麗\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You sound exactly like my daughter Scarlett.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.94,0:30:17.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她和你一般大 但她是我知道的最老成的小姑娘了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}She's around your age, but she's the oldest little girl I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:19.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我深信她因為每一件我做的錯事\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I think deep down she blames herself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.85,0:30:22.68,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而在心裏責怪她自己\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}for everything that's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.69,0:30:27.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但錯在我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But it's me,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.95,0:30:30.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不是她\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.49,0:30:33.26,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,同樣的 錯在他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And it's him,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.29,0:30:35.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不是你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.96,0:30:38.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.40,0:30:42.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你一點都不像我父親\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You're nothing like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.59,0:30:47.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當我還小的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.01,0:30:51.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我爸爸告訴我他等不及我長大\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}my daddy told me he couldn't wait for me to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.48,0:30:59.79,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他跟我說我會成為他的小淑女\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He told me I was gonna be his little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.96,0:31:05.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他說話的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The way he said it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.52,0:31:07.76,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,讓我的胃都疼起來了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}it made my stomach hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.79,0:31:10.86,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,令我不想入眠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It got so I didn't want to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.98,0:31:14.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為我每睜開眼一次 都離長大近了一天\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}'cause every time I woke up I was a day closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.29,0:31:16.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,有一天他把我留在車裏\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}One day he left me in a car
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.53,0:31:19.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,自己去科爾特茲喝酒\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}while he went drinking at the Cortez.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.29,0:31:32.18,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那天熱瘋了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It was so crazy hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.22,0:31:35.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,車裏就像烤箱一樣\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was like a pizza in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.05,0:31:37.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但我沒有打開窗戶 我什麼都沒說\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But I didn't open the window, and I didn't say a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.52,0:31:38.75,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為我想\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}because I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.87,0:31:41.46,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,也許有一種我不必長大的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}maybe there was a way I didn't have to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.54,0:31:50.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但我找到了另一種方法\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But I found another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.43,0:31:53.00,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,現在我想長大可能也沒有那麼糟\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Now I think maybe growing up wouldn't have been so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.04,0:31:55.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,至少不會比現在更糟\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It can't be worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.84,0:31:57.34,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,雷恩 我不明白\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Wren, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.37,0:31:59.51,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你是在告訴我殺手是你父親嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Are you telling me it's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.54,0:32:00.68,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他是殺手\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He's the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.80,0:32:03.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不 他很早就去世了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No. He died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.67,0:32:05.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我只是 我只是煩死這一切了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm just... I'm so sick of this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.58,0:32:07.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我一點都不想再捲入到裏面了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't want it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.05,0:32:08.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那麼就放手吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Then let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.39,0:32:10.18,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-告訴我他是誰 -我不能\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- Tell me who he is. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.30,0:32:11.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要保護一個\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why are you protecting someone
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.47,0:32:12.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,根本就不值得你這麼做的人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}who doesn't deserve anything from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.09,0:32:13.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你不會相信我的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.04,0:32:14.76,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他會一直殺人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}He's going to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.83,0:32:17.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,除非你幫我阻止他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}killing people unless you help me stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.38,0:32:20.46,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,把我從這兒弄出去 我就告訴你他住在哪兒\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Get me out of here, and I'll show you where he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.54,0:32:23.43,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們現在不是在玩遊戲 雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We're not playing a game here, Wren.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.47,0:32:25.60,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,也許該是他被抓的時候了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Maybe it's time he got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:39.19,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我終於開始\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm finally beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:41.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,感覺到生命回流到我身上了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}to feel the life return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.17,0:32:47.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我看起來怎樣\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.28,0:32:49.00,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,糟透了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.91,0:32:53.78,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你就是在誇大其詞\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You're being dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.81,0:32:56.66,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她只比老鼠好那麼一點兒\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That was little better than the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.24,0:32:58.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們需要更多\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.85,0:33:00.12,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.15,0:33:02.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,再多一百倍\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}A hundred times more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.56,0:33:05.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這種飢渴\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}This thirst--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:07.72,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是沒法滿足的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}it's unslakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.76,0:33:09.79,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.83,0:33:12.29,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,婊子養的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.33,0:33:15.00,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們被困在這鬼地方多久了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}How long have we been trapped in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.03,0:33:17.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,啊 太久了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Aah. Too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.47,0:33:22.84,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我要 把那個男人的頭撕下來\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I am going... to rip that man's head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.87,0:33:25.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我覺得他早就死了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I imagine that he is long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.71,0:33:29.88,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,而且老實說 都怪你害我們陷入這樣的困境\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And in truth, you are as much to blame for our predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.91,0:33:32.51,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你和你那隻小老鼠\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You and your little mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.55,0:33:33.98,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她跟這個無關\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}She had no part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.02,0:33:35.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們不需要她\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We didn't need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.64,0:33:38.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們有錢 我們有整個世界\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We had money. We had the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.40,0:33:40.11,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,永恆的生命\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Life everlasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.23,0:33:42.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,但你想要你的寵物\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But you craved your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:45.19,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她值得嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Was she worth it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.23,0:33:47.70,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,看看我們\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Look at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.73,0:33:49.73,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,「偉大的情聖」\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}"The Great Lover,"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.77,0:33:53.90,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這張為女人狂熱渴求\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}that magnificent face that women lusted after,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.94,0:33:58.94,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,又陷她們於死境的絕美面孔 現在卻變成奇醜無比的怪物\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}killed themselves over, reduced to a grotesque monstrosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.97,0:34:01.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們的生命被偷走了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Our lives stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.42,0:34:04.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,一切都沒有了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Everything gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.31,0:34:06.98,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你是對的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.02,0:34:09.52,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,原諒我 親愛的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Forgive me, amore.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.55,0:34:11.95,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我太蠢了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I was foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.99,0:34:17.12,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我保證 我們會重新收回失去的一切\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I promise, we will reclaim all that we have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:19.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-你在做夢 -你等著看吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- You are dreaming. - You will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.67,0:34:22.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們的生命會比曾經\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Our life will be far more glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.53,0:34:25.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,更加輝煌\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}than it ever was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.60,0:34:30.34,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,走錯房間了 蠢蛋\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Wrong room, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.37,0:34:33.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,夥計 那些讀書俱樂部的女士們都趴在我身上\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Dude, those book club ladies were all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.04,0:34:35.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你看見那個紅頭髮舔我的蛋了嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Did you see that redhead lick my balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.04,0:34:36.44,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你他媽就是一坨屎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You're so full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:39.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼 這兒只有一張床\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The hell? There's only one bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.05,0:34:40.85,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我才不跟你們這群傻逼分享我的床\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm not sharing a room with one of you cumsicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.88,0:34:42.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-啊 -你睡地上\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- Ah... - You're sleeping on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:45.29,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,脫衣舞男總是得到最糟糕的房間 哈\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Strippers always get the shittiest rooms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.65,0:34:48.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,多有趣的生物啊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What curious creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.02,0:34:51.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,像克羅索斯巨人重返人間\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Like the Colossus come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:55.53,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,他們血液奔流的聲音簡直震耳欲聾\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The gush of their blood is deafening.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:34:59.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼會拒絕來自神的禮物呢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Who are we to deny a gift from the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.97,0:35:09.01,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:10.78,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,威靈頓肯定\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Surely the Wellington
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.81,0:35:13.05,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,在變冷吧 馬奇先生\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}is getting cold, Mr. March.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.77,0:35:16.62,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,幾乎不需擔心 埃弗斯女士\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Hardly a concern, Ms. Evers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.25,0:35:34.03,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,或許你的客人要多注意\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Perhaps your guest should be mindful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.07,0:35:36.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,她來訪的時間\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}of the time she's expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.44,0:35:38.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不認為\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I don't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.10,0:35:39.38,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我在意你的語氣 埃弗斯女士\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I care for your tone, Ms. Evers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.48,0:35:41.79,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這座房子的女主人值得更多的尊重\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The lady of the house deserves more respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.91,0:35:42.98,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是的 馬奇先生\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes, Mr. March.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.11,0:35:47.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你現在離開一會\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}You should be elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.38,0:35:52.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,最親愛的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Dearest!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.95,0:35:55.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,謝謝你今晚和我見面 詹姆斯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Thank you for seeing me tonight, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.29,0:35:57.02,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我知道這早了一周\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I know it's a week early.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.06,0:35:58.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不不 胡說\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Mm. Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.61,0:36:01.36,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,無論什麼時候我都很樂意主辦我們的晚餐\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'd be delighted to host our meal on any night you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.39,0:36:03.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們可以不再一月一次 改成一晚一次\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}We could have it nightly instead of monthly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.28,0:36:05.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,只是說說\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.10,0:36:06.96,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,一個月一次 詹姆斯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Once a month, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.00,0:36:09.20,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這是我們的安排\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That's our arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.23,0:36:11.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我有太多事情要忙了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm far too busy for anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.34,0:36:12.54,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.66,0:36:14.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你要來點阿瑪尼亞克酒嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Would you like an Armagnac?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.25,0:36:17.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-我要來一杯 -不了 謝謝\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- I'm having one. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.79,0:36:35.99,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.03,0:36:39.63,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我想親自告訴你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I wanted to tell you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:42.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我計劃再次結婚\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I plan to marry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.30,0:36:45.97,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好極了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.00,0:36:48.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我當然會替你感到高興了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Why, I couldn't be more pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.11,0:36:50.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們慶祝一下吧 好嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Let's have a toast, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.11,0:36:51.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那個幸運的男人是誰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Who's the lucky fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:55.08,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我會送他一些牛排\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'd like to send him some steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.11,0:36:56.95,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,威爾·德雷克\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Will Drake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.98,0:36:59.18,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,啊 好的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.69,0:37:01.28,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那個買下我旅館\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That light-in-the-loafers
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.32,0:37:02.50,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,的同性戀\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}fellow that bought my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.62,0:37:05.09,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,很好 親愛的 很好\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Very good, darling. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.12,0:37:06.92,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我可以建議你殺他的時候\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Might I suggest that when you murder him,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.96,0:37:08.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,別在旅館裏動手嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}you do so off the property?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.34,0:37:09.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,永生的日子裏\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It'd be damned awkward
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.59,0:37:11.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,經常撞見他會尷尬死的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}to keep running into him for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.65,0:37:14.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,為什麼你認為我會傷害他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And what makes you think I mean to do him harm?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.16,0:37:18.07,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我雖然死了 親愛的 我並不傻\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I'm dead, dear. Not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.10,0:37:21.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我不是找到真愛了呢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And how do you know I haven't found love?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.07,0:37:25.37,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,也許是第一次遇上真愛\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}True love maybe for the very first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.01,0:37:29.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,肯定不是第一次\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Surely not for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.85,0:37:32.18,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,馬奇夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Mrs. March.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.21,0:37:36.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我一直對你恪守誠實 詹姆斯\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I've always been scrupulously honest with you, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.59,0:37:39.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我從來沒有偽裝過我的感受\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I never pretended more than I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.19,0:37:43.33,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我也從來沒有聲稱過我愛你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}And I never claimed to love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.08,0:37:46.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:51.47,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.54,0:38:04.71,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,只是我並不是在說我自己\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}But then, I wasn't referring to myself now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.75,0:38:07.31,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.35,0:38:10.12,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你什麼意思\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.98,0:38:19.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我以為我可以讓你愛我\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I thought I could make you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.09,0:38:21.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我以為如果我能給你一切\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I thought if I gave you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.43,0:38:24.13,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你的小心臟所渴望的東西\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}your little heart desired--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.17,0:38:28.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,財富 舒適\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}riches, comfort...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.27,0:38:32.04,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,這個旅館\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}this hotel--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.07,0:38:34.64,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,沒有一樣可以感動你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}but none of it moved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.25,0:38:40.39,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我永遠也無法與那大銀屏上的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I could never compete with the shadow of a god
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.51,0:38:42.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,上帝的影子相匹敵\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}on a screen, 20 feet tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.85,0:38:46.42,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不 讓他走\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No, let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.45,0:38:48.25,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,-放開她 -放開他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}- Let her go! - Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.71,0:38:53.16,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我懷疑\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I have a sneaking suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.19,0:38:55.40,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你可能會錯過你的火車\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}you're going to miss your train.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.29,0:39:23.82,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.13,0:39:29.36,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.05,0:39:34.83,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,魯迪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Rudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.49,0:39:38.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我們在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:42.30,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.33,0:40:48.49,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.77,0:40:51.24,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你的上帝\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Your god.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.83,0:40:55.88,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,因為我的女王 被困在我所建造的\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Trapped within the walls of the palace I built
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.91,0:40:58.55,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,宮殿的圍牆裏\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}for my queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.42,0:41:03.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,那就是後面的秘密嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}That's what was back there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.69,0:41:05.98,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不 再是了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Not... anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.25,0:41:30.65,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.68,0:41:33.21,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,走\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.06,0:41:48.73,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好了 我帶你出來了\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}All right, I got you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.76,0:41:51.23,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,現在你帶我去見他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Now you take me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:52.63,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Wren...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.67,0:41:53.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,然後我們需要回家\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Then we need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.05,0:41:55.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你家在哪\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.60,0:41:57.17,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,科爾特茲旅館\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}The Cortez.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.49,0:41:59.93,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,好 別害怕\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}All right, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.05,0:42:01.41,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,當我找到他 我會把他\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}When I find him, I'm gonna bury him
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.49,0:42:03.71,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,深埋 他再也不會重見天日\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}in a hole so deep, he'll never see the light of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.83,0:42:06.81,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,是時候讓他停止\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}It's time to make him stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.85,0:42:09.35,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,你會殺了他嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Will you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.38,0:42:11.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,如果我必須要做的話\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}If I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.49,0:42:13.45,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我真的喜歡你\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:17.22,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,我不想就這麼結束\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}I hate to see it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.53,0:42:21.06,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,再見了 約翰\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Good-bye, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.10,0:42:22.80,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,雷恩\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}Wren!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.83,0:42:25.57,SSK-C,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\bord2\fs37}No!
